1. *Pogledamo* li to malo bolje, shvatit ćemo smisao. (Let's look at this a little closer and we'll understand the meaning.)

2. On je *pogledao* u nju i osmehnuo se. (He looked at her and smiled.)

3. Učenici su *pogledali* u profesora očekujući odgovor. (The students looked at the teacher expecting an answer.)

4. Ona je *pogledala* u njega sa sumnjom u očima. (She looked at him with suspicion in her eyes.)

5. *Pogledajmo* šta je tu napisano. (Let's look at what's written here.)